msgctxt "landingFaqEyebrow"
msgid "FAQ"
msgstr "FAQ"

msgctxt "landingFaqHeading"
msgid "Common questions."
msgstr "Pertanyaan umum."

msgctxt "landingFaqItems.0.0"
msgid "What is AWCMS-Micro?"
msgstr "Apa itu AWCMS-Micro?"

msgctxt "landingFaqItems.0.1"
msgid "AWCMS-Micro is a downstream overlay of EmDash CMS, delivering CMS-powered public websites on Cloudflare with D1, R2, and Workers."
msgstr "AWCMS-Micro adalah overlay downstream dari EmDash CMS yang menghadirkan website publik bertenaga CMS di Cloudflare dengan D1, R2, dan Workers."

msgctxt "landingFaqItems.1.0"
msgid "How is content managed?"
msgstr "Bagaimana konten dikelola?"

msgctxt "landingFaqItems.1.1"
msgid "All content — pages, posts, news, galleries, and widgets — is managed from the EmDash admin panel and published directly to the public site."
msgstr "Semua konten — halaman, pos, berita, galeri, dan widget — dikelola dari panel admin EmDash dan dipublikasikan langsung ke situs publik."

msgctxt "landingFaqItems.2.0"
msgid "Is bilingual content supported?"
msgstr "Apakah konten bilingual didukung?"

msgctxt "landingFaqItems.2.1"
msgid "Yes. AWCMS-Micro supports EN and ID locales with row-per-locale content in D1 and locale-aware public routing."
msgstr "Ya. AWCMS-Micro mendukung lokal EN dan ID dengan konten row-per-locale di D1 dan routing publik berbasis lokal."

msgctxt "landingFaqItems.3.0"
msgid "Can I add my own features?"
msgstr "Apakah bisa menambah fitur sendiri?"

msgctxt "landingFaqItems.3.1"
msgid "Yes. AWCMS-Micro uses an approved plugin and template overlay model so you can add features without modifying EmDash core."
msgstr "Ya. AWCMS-Micro menggunakan model overlay plugin dan template yang disetujui sehingga fitur bisa ditambah tanpa memodifikasi core EmDash."

